00:46:53.090 --> 00:46:55.519
Because it seems to me
that a lot of people

00:46:55.519 --> 00:46:58.060
think it has to do with being
very good at math and so forth,

00:46:58.060 --> 00:46:59.950
but it seems like the
psychological aspect

00:46:59.950 --> 00:47:03.140
and the discipline aspect is
actually as important or maybe

00:47:03.140 --> 00:47:04.740
more.

00:47:04.740 --> 00:47:06.490
JOHN HEINS: And I can
start with that one,

00:47:06.490 --> 00:47:09.060
and that's what I would
say is that I think what--

00:47:09.060 --> 00:47:11.010
